@page "/terms"

<PageTitle>Terms of Service - TodoX</PageTitle>

<MudContainer MaxWidth="MaxWidth.Medium" Class="py-8">
    <MudPaper Class="todox-card pa-6" Rounded="true">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h4" Class="todox-page-title">Terms of Service</MudText>
        <MudText Typo="Typo.caption" Class="todox-page-subtitle">Last updated: July 2026</MudText>

        <MudDivider Class="my-4" />

        <MudStack Spacing="3">
            <MudText>
                These Terms govern the use of TodoX, a SaaS platform for AI content generation, video rendering,
                social page management, and publishing automation.
            </MudText>

            <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">Use of Service</MudText>
            <MudText>
                Users are responsible for the content they create, upload, render, and publish through TodoX.
                Users must comply with applicable laws and the terms of connected platforms such as Facebook,
                Instagram, TikTok, and other third-party services.
            </MudText>

            <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">Connected Social Accounts</MudText>
            <MudText>
                By connecting a social page or account, the user authorizes TodoX to perform actions permitted
                by the granted permissions, such as listing pages, preparing posts, and publishing content selected
                by the user.
            </MudText>

            <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">Prohibited Use</MudText>
            <MudText>
                Users must not use TodoX to publish illegal, misleading, infringing, harmful, or unauthorized content.
                Users must not connect accounts or pages they do not have permission to manage.
            </MudText>

            <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">Service Availability</MudText>
            <MudText>
                TodoX may depend on third-party APIs and infrastructure. Availability, rate limits, and platform
                policies may affect some features.
            </MudText>

            <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">Data and Deletion</MudText>
            <MudText>
                Users may request deletion of account and connected platform data according to our
                <MudLink Href="/data-deletion">User Data Deletion</MudLink> instructions.
            </MudText>

            <MudText Typo="Typo.h6">Contact</MudText>
            <MudText>For questions about these Terms, contact: support@todox.vn</MudText>
        </MudStack>
    </MudPaper>
</MudContainer>
